[Voronezh is in the Central Black Earth Economic Region (CBEER) of Russia
located to the south of Moscow. Of interest is the suggestion that the wild
mushrooms may have been purchased rather than harvested individually by
family or friends of the cases. More information on this outbreak would be
greatly appreciated. - Mod.MPP]
